  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为BYOD远程办公场景设计一个AppGate SDP架构图。核心需求是外部用户通过AVD接入，然后由SDP Controller统一管控两个网关平面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BYOD",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL",
        "DATA_PLANE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为左侧是外部BYOD用户，中间经过AVD作为入口，然后连接到SDP Controller。数据平面部分您提到两个网关，是GW1和GW2分别对应不同的资源类型吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2",
        "BYOD",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GW1负责Protected Resources，GW2负责Protected Services。GW1下面挂DOMAIN、DEV、SEG三个网段，GW2下面挂DOMAIN SERVICES、DEV SERVICES和HWIL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2",
        "DOMAIN",
        "DEV",
        "SEG",
        "DOMSVC",
        "DEVSVC",
        "HWIL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用子图把DATA_PLANE包起来，里面分左右两个lane：GW1_LANE放资源层，GW2_LANE放服务层，都用TB方向排列。这样结构清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DATA_PLANE",
        "GW1_LANE",
        "GW2_LANE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但GW1_LANE和GW2_LANE之间要用LR方向，这样左右对比更直观。另外每个节点都要标注双网段：201.x和202.x的地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1_LANE",
        "GW2_LANE",
        "201.x",
        "202.x"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。现在DATA_PLANE内部是LR方向，两个lane都是TB方向。AVD节点我标注了201.1.2.0/24和202.1.2.0/24，Controller是201.0.1.0/24和202.0.1.0/24。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AVD",
        "CTRL",
        "DATA_PLANE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接关系需要仔细处理。BYOD到AVD走Internet，这是第一条线。AVD出来后要同时连Controller和两个Gateway，但协议端口要注意。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BYOD",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL",
        "GW1",
        "GW2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "AVD到Controller、GW1、GW2都是tcp/udp 443加上udp 53对吧？那Controller到两个Gateway的连接呢，也是同样的端口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AVD",
        "CTRL",
        "GW1",
        "GW2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，所有控制通道都是tcp/udp 443 + udp 53。但GW1和GW2到后端资源是全端口开放，标注为All Ports。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2",
        "DOMAIN",
        "DEV",
        "SEG",
        "DOMSVC",
        "DEVSVC",
        "HWIL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接关系已画好。GW1到DOMAIN、DEV、SEG都是All Ports，GW2到DOMSVC、DEVSVC、HWIL也是全端口。现在需要处理视觉样式，让不同角色有区分度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2",
        "DOMAIN",
        "DEV",
        "SEG",
        "DOMSVC",
        "DEVSVC",
        "HWIL"
