      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "具体色值您有要求吗？我打算SDP用d7f3ff填充、1f7ea8描边，BYOD用ffe9d6和e07a2c，AVD用e6f7e6和2f8f2f。资源和服务都用6f3cc3描边，但填充色区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sdp",
