      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。CTRL、GW1、GW2归为sdp类，BYOD是enduser，AVD是client，DOMAIN/DEV/SEG是sdpg，DOMSVC/DEVSVC/HWIL是sdpt。所有classDef都设置了2px描边宽度。",
