      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查下GW1和GW2的网段标注，应该是201.0.2.0/24和202.0.2.0/24对应GW1，201.0.3.0/24和202.0.3.0/24对应GW2吧？",
